{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b79578d9a7","title":"攻击党委团委的言论","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7fea973659","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"b79578d9a7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0aeba49c5c","name":"龙国坤"},{"id":"3d25ad450b","name":"陈汉良"},{"id":"4771ddecd4","name":"丁少飞"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"a9a9412980","name":"许国坤"},{"id":"ba26f455f4","name":"章永良"},{"id":"feb49b1d89","name":"曹荫浓"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f1f6435d2d","type":"title","text":"攻击党委团委的言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"95778d5d2a","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院许国坤曹荫浓丁少飞龙国坤陈汉良章永良","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"423411fb19","type":"appellation","text":"许国坤说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"2470b4814d","type":"appellation","text":"“团委和党委是一鼻孔出气，和党委会意见完全一致，就不能代表同学的意见，团委会就不能代表我们。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"6cb34dba21","type":"appellation","text":"曹荫浓：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"2680bf12d1","type":"appellation","text":"“党员起了便衣警察的作用，把党员污蔑为吃他心肝，吸尽他血液，敲他骨髓的魔鬼，石象，便衣警察，毒蛇……","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"69fe433b0e","type":"appellation","text":"“高级干部每月拿几百元是变质，是喝农民血，吃农民肉。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"5c3810422c","type":"appellation","text":"“党委腐化了”。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"636abad4af","type":"appellation","text":"“党委这么多缺点，象尹凤翔这样的人能领导地院？”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"fffcb62ee1","type":"subtitle","text":"“社会主义制度下的革命是必然的。”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"9497606d68","type":"appellation","text":"丁少飞说：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"be45e40107","type":"appellation","text":"“党员干部是留声机，首长，大人，机器人。”","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"9158e934f7","type":"appellation","text":"“高级干部也没有什么，和我们一样是糊里糊涂，不要把他们看得太高了。”","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"403847749b","type":"appellation","text":"“郭沫若是三角脑袋，恨不得拿铲子把他轧死。”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"edb2607614","type":"appellation","text":"龙国坤说：","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"aee05c9c75","type":"appellation","text":"“党员不体会中央精神，盲目的维护党委，这不是真正的维护党的利益，不能正确执行党的政策”他又说：“我把人分为三种（一）偏激冒险的人（二）四平八稳的人（三）麻木不问世事的人。党员是四平八稳的人，是不独立思考的，上级说什么就是什么的人，只会照决议办事的人，或者只是善于放弃自己意见的人，团支部，党员，思想束缚很大，职位越高，受的束缚越大，本来活跃的都变的死气沉沉了。”","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"ba69a97bcb","type":"appellation","text":"陈汉良说：","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"3924479f41","type":"appellation","text":"“贪污腐化，强奸妇女都是共产党员，××党团员是狐群狗党，党员是饭桶。”","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"04f7293651","type":"appellation","text":"章永良：","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"},{"id":"81a02748be","type":"appellation","text":"“一些党员感情用事，排挤我，自己好工作因此反感。”","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7"}],"page":{"id":"2f48bf2df1","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b79578d9a7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}